data.title: Spotify launches new Disney music hub: Listen here
data.meta_description: The music hub will be a destination for Disney music that suits every mood or moment of day.
data.text:
Disney fans, rejoice!

Introducing #SpotifyxDisney: A first-of-its-kind music hub filled with just about every song, lyric and tune from across the entire Disney library, from Star Wars to Frozen.

Listeners in the United States, Canada, South Africa, The United Kingdom, Ireland, Australia and New Zealand can simply search “Disney” and find a special home for all the music behind some of their all-time favorite Disney movies, television shows, and more.

Everything from chart-topping Marvel movie soundtracks and full scores from Disney classics are being made available too.

This also marks the first time Spotify has create a hub page for a brand, and there's something for Disney fans of all ages.

With more selections being added periodically, the music hub will also be a destination for Disney music that suits every mood or moment of day.

Here's a sampling of playlists from the all-new Spotify Disney Hub:

Best of Star Wars

Includes some of the most well-known Oscar and Grammy-winning score cues the world over.

Marvel Music

All the best songs and score from all your favorite Marvel films and shows.

Disney Hits

The top songs from the biggest Disney and Pixar Films.

Disney Favorites

Everyone’s favorite current tunes, plus songs you loved as a child.

Disney Classics

A nostalgic playlist that includes songs from Disney Parks, live action and animated classic soundtracks, and songs from Disney Channel Original Movies.

Disney Sing-Alongs

Songs perfect for sing-alongs; on the road or anywhere.

Disney Princess

From Belle to Cinderella to Ariel and Moana, Disney Princess includes love ballads as well as coming-of-age anthems.

Disney is the parent company of ABC News and "Good Morning America."
